<!--
  Vision-Sync sitemap.
  Two kinds of URLs live here:
    1. Static pages  -> these map to explicit routes in src/App.tsx (Homepage + marketing pages).
    2. Project pages -> these map to rows in the `projects` table, served by the
                        /:projectRoute catch-all (src/components/DynamicProjectDetail.tsx),
                        which matches the URL slug against projects.route.

  TO REGENERATE THE PROJECT PAGES BLOCK (keep it in sync as projects are added/removed):
    Query the live DB for the canonical list of routes:
        select route from projects order by route;
    Then emit one url entry per row, with loc = https://www.vision-sync.co + route
        (priority 0.7, changefreq weekly).
    Leave the Homepage + Static Pages blocks alone — those are driven by App.tsx routes, not the DB.
    A URL that is neither an App.tsx route nor a projects.route will 404 to the
    "Project Not Found" fallback, so it must NOT appear here.
-->
